00:28:21,952 --> 00:28:23,985
But of course, milord.

517
00:28:25,422 --> 00:28:27,522
Oh, Manticore!

518
00:28:31,094 --> 00:28:34,196
No. No, no, no.
The real Manticore.

519
00:28:34,198 --> 00:28:36,431
The fearless adventurer.

520
00:28:36,433 --> 00:28:38,569
