You need to plan for that.

529
00:28:58,622 --> 00:29:01,757
Well, maybe your mother should
get her own car!

530
00:29:01,759 --> 00:29:03,258
Your fearlessness?

531
00:29:03,260 --> 00:29:05,828
My brother and I seek a map
