desire right here. Behold!

534
00:29:13,303 --> 00:29:15,771
Oh. That's
a children's menu.

535
00:29:15,773 --> 00:29:18,740
Isn't that fun? They're all
based on my old maps.

536
00:29:18,742 --> 00:29:19,809
Uh, now...

537
00:29:19,811 --> 00:29:21,142
The great Manticore
sends you

538
00:29:21,144 --> 00:29:22,879
