ma'am...

560
00:30:11,528 --> 00:30:12,762
What are you doing?

561
00:30:12,764 --> 00:30:14,396
Kid, this is not
a good time.

562
00:30:14,398 --> 00:30:17,065
Ugh. I'm giving this place
a one-star review.

563
00:30:17,067 --> 00:30:19,334
It's just,
I've never met my dad and...

564
00:30:19,336 --> 00:30:20,535
Look,
I'm sorry about that.

