to get gas?

743
00:38:16,847 --> 00:38:20,617
Oh!
I like your thinking, young mage.

744
00:38:23,154 --> 00:38:24,119
Growth spell!

745
00:38:24,121 --> 00:38:26,388
We grow the can,
and then the gas inside

746
00:38:26,390 --> 00:38:27,555
