747
00:38:27,557 --> 00:38:30,259
Uh, that's kind of
a weird idea.

748
00:38:30,261 --> 00:38:32,161
I know!
I like it, too.

749
00:38:32,163 --> 00:38:33,429
Okay.

750
00:38:33,431 --> 00:38:35,864
